data.title: CORPORATIONS & CORPORATE FOUNDATIONS
data.text:
That the University has earned a place of prominence among institutions of higher education is a tribute to the spirit of cooperation between the institution and its corporate partners.

Through the decade, corporate benefactors have helped change the face of the University campus, making possible such new facilities as the MBNA Career Services Center and the Delaware Biotechnology Institute.

We thank our partners in the corporate world, understanding that continued corporate support will help improve our University for generations of students to come.
